WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
This is the moment gunshots rang out in Times Square,

2
00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.000
sending hundreds of people running.

3
00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
I checked my phone, I see Instagram shots fired near Times Square.

4
00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:18.000
Earthcam video captured the shooter and the chaotic scene at 44th Street and 7th Avenue.

5
00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:23.000
People racing away while NYPD officers rushed in.

6
00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:26.000
People were running to cover for safety.

7
00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:29.000
The shooter can be seen aiming and firing the gun into the crowd

8
00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:33.000
before turning to flee the scene, running right into a police officer,

9
00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:36.000
barely slowing down before taking off again.

10
00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:38.000
More police joined the foot pursuit.

11
00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:42.000
Police say there was some kind of fight just after 3.30 Thursday afternoon

12
00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:46.000
and they took into custody a 17-year-old suspected of firing the shots.

13
00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:49.000
Nobody was struck, police said they recovered the gun.

14
00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:52.000
A block to the west at 45th Street and 8th Avenue,

15
00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:54.000
a 26-year-old man was slashed.

16
00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:57.000
Police are now working to determine if there is some kind of connection.

17
00:00:57.000 --> 00:01:00.000
The victim is stable, he was taken to the hospital.

18
00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:04.000
And that 17-year-old who is suspected of firing the shots

19
00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:07.000
is in custody, this morning charges against him are pending.

